---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ThemeSwitcher from "../components/ThemeToggle.astro";
import "../css/index.css";
const title = "About - Ekeopre Beredugo";
const description =
	"Ekeopre Beredugo is a frontend web developer that specializes in creating quality high converting websites.";
const author = "Ekeopre Beredugo";
const scrollToTop = "#about";
---

<BaseLayout
	title={title}
	description={description}
	author={author}
	scrollToTop={scrollToTop}
>
	<main class="container" id="about">
		<h1 class="main-title title">About</h1>
		<p class="about-me">
			Hello, I'm Ekeopre Beredugo, a frontend developer based in Nigeria. I'm
			passionate about building beautiful and accessibile websites for personal
			brands and businesses. Every project I undertake is a canvas for
			innovation. Whether it's a portfolio showcasing a budding artist's
			creations or an e-commerce platform revolutionizing local businesses, I
			approach each endeavor with an artist's eye and a coder's precision. With
			every pixel I place, every animation I design, and every interaction I
			craft, my goal is to forge connections – connections that bridge brands
			and their audiences in meaningful ways.
		</p>
		<h2 class="title">How it all started</h2>
		<p class="about-me">
			I began my journey into frontend development back in 2020. It all started
			with a simple curiosity about how websites are created. I went looking
			free online resources to learn HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, slowly building
			up my skills. As time went on, I wanted to learn even more so I enrolled
			in paid courses that deepened my knowledge and taught me how to create
			websites that not only looked great but also worked smoothly ad wre
			accessible. In addition to the basics, I explored tools like WordPress,
			React, and Astro. These tools added extra layers to my skills. WordPress
			made building sites easier, React let me add cool features, and Astro
			helped speed up websites. I won't deny there were challenges along the
			way. Coding is like solving puzzles – sometimes it's tricky, but with each
			challenge, I got better and I have gone on to create great websites.
		</p>

		<h2 class="title">What motivates me</h2>
		<p class="about-me">
			Passion is my driving force – the very essence that fuels my dedication to
			the craft. Through countless lines of code and late-night brainstorming
			sessions, I've cultivated a deep appreciation for the intricate dance
			between aesthetics and functionality. The ability to translate a brand's
			vision into a digital masterpiece that resonates with its audience is a
			challenge I wholeheartedly embrace. I'm always seeking to learn and
			contribute, so, whether you're a fellow developer, a visionary brand
			owner, or simply an enthusiast exploring the digital realm, I invite you
			to join me on this journey. Let's create not just websites, but digital
			experiences that resonate, inspire, and endure.
		</p>
		<a href="/">Go to homepage</a>

		<ThemeSwitcher />
	</main>
</BaseLayout>

<script></script>

<style>
	* {
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	.dark {
		background-color: var(--darkTheme-color);
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	/* archivo-black-regular - latin */
	@font-face {
		font-family: "Archivo Black";
		font-style: normal;
		font-weight: 400;
		src: url("/assets/fonts/archivo-black-v17-latin/archivo-black-v17-latin-regular.eot"); /* IE9 Compat Modes */
		src: local(""),
			url("/assets/fonts/archivo-black-v17-latin/archivo-black-v17-latin-regular.eot?#iefix")
				format("embedded-opentype"),
			/* IE6-IE8 */
				url("/assets/fonts/archivo-black-v17-latin//archivo-black-v17-latin-regular.woff2")
				format("woff2"),
			/* Super Modern Browsers */
				url("/assets/fonts/archivo-black-v17-latin/archivo-black-v17-latin-regular.woff")
				format("woff"),
			/* Modern Browsers */
				url("/assets/fonts/archivo-black-v17-latin//archivo-black-v17-latin-regular.ttf")
				format("truetype"),
			/* Safari, Android, iOS */
				url("/assets/fonts/archivo-black-v17-latin//archivo-black-v17-latin-regular.svg#ArchivoBlack")
				format("svg"); /* Legacy iOS */
	}

	html {
		width: 100%;
	}

	body {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: space-between;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 80%;
	}
	.container h1 {
		margin: 20px auto;
		font-family: "Archivo Black";
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: 3.5rem;
	}

	.container h2 {
		margin: 20px auto;
		font-family: "Archivo Black";
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.container p {
		font-size: 18px;
		padding-bottom: 2%;
	}

	.container a {
		color: var(--darkTheme-color);
		text-decoration: underline;
		font-size: 24px;
	}

	.container a:hover {
		background-color: var(--darkTheme-color);
		color: #ffffff;
	}
	@media (min-width: 800px) {
		.container p {
			font-size: 24px;
		}
	}
	@media (max-width: 1250px) {
		.container h1 {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 820px) {
		.container {
			margin: 5% 0;
		}
		.container h1 {
			font-size: 30px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 599px) {
		.container {
			margin: 30% 1.5rem;
		}
		.container h1 {
			font-size: 25px;
		}
	}

	@media (min-width: 600px) {
		.container {
			padding: 10% 3rem;
		}
	}
</style>
